these specs for the DC-4.

1168
01:32:44,179 --> 01:32:47,637
Ava, what do you think about
Trans World Airlines?

1169
01:32:47,816 --> 01:32:50,341
Transcontinental and Western
doesn't fit anymore.

1170
01:32:50,519 --> 01:32:53,386
