General McEwan. Colonel Bertrang.
Thanks for coming down.

1303
01:41:46,254 --> 01:41:48,415
Odie, you reading me okay?

1304
01:41:48,590 --> 01:41:49,818
Yeah, you're A-okay.

1305
01:41:55,463 --> 01:41:58,660
<i>All right, flight controls are active.</i>
